column1: #Text=" Congratulations Emmanuel Macron ! Let 's meet soon , and keep working to grow and strengthen the deep ties between Canada and France " ( ( fr))French language : ‍Félicitations Emmanuel Macron ! Rencontrons-nous rapidement et continuons à renforcer les liens de fraternité entre le Canada et la France , Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau tweeted .
#Text=German chancellor Angela Merkel congratulated Macron via a telephone call .
#Text=French parliamentary elections are to be held in June , and Emmanuel Macron , who describes himself as " neither left nor right " does not have a party in the parliament .
